Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.42,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,那么开始授课了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:11.13,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,准备好了吗? 小点同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:12.10,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:15.66,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,潜水时要准备的东西有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:20.14,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,泳衣 香波 洗发素
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.06,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,潜水日志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:23.90,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,然后就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.65,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:30.06,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,更换用的小裤裤是以草莓巧克力为设计初衷的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.66,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,有着粉红色缎带和花边的丝绸质地...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:34.45,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,你们在说些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:42.60,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}つま先からちょっとずつ生まれ変わってく気分　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:42.60,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,有一种由脚尖开始 慢慢重生的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:49.52,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}名前はまだない  始まった物语　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:49.52,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,故事才刚开始 还没有标题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:59.78,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}最初の1ページには  风の中に立つ人が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:59.78,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的一页上是谁迎风站立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:13.25,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}ああ　夏草の匂い　湿った空気と　打ち寄せる波の音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:13.25,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 夏草的清香 湿润的空气 拍岸的海浪声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:25.47,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}ああ　この海が何とつながってるのか　考えているの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:25.47,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我不禁思考 这片大海究竟与何相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:35.44,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}今しかできないことをすぐにやらなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:35.44,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,只有现在能做的事 必须立刻行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:41.36,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}几千の云をかき分けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:41.36,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,拨开万干的云层
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:45.07,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}駆け上がる気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:45.07,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,不断攀升的情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:50.16,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}こんな私がいたなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:50.16,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还有这样的我存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:58.38,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}始まった物语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:58.38,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,故事才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:12.23,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}最初の1ページには　风の中に立つ私がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:12.23,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的一页上 有我迎风站立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:19.70,Amanchu_Ep_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(446,430)\fn@宋体\pos(770.667,382)\frz270.2}跃跃欲试与放弃的心境的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:26.56,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,本人小点～～大木双叶将在下周迎来泳池实践
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:30.64,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,今天前来参观海边的实际潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:36.15,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,没想到我会迎来这样的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.62,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:43.33,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,不过没想到光和姑娘你还成了朋友呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:44.72,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.59,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,还有一个出乎意料的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.62,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,闪光的奶奶...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.67,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,竟然是当时的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.73,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,这是何等的命中注定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:05.64,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,要上咯 好久没做指导者了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:05.64,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}instructor:潜水指导者/潜水教练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:09.22,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,咦? 闪光要给今天的客人做向导吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:10.29,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.74,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,不过主要还是束子君负责向导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.73,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,束...子...君...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.69,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,附近潜水器材店的店长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.61,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我是辅助向导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:21.99,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.55,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,虽然有点紧张 但我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:31.08,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,将来成为这里本地的职业指导者 可是我的梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.29,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:36.11,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,这就已经确定将来的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:41.43,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我还一次都没有下过水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.02,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,真是了不起啊 闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.12,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,加油! 闪光!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.77,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:08.90,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:14.75,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,这边的两位就是今天的客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.21,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,还请多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.07,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我才是请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:24.02,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,那我们这就开始装备 把器材背起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.31,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.68,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,伙伴确认也请仔细地做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.68,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}buddy check:伙伴确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.82,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.44,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,伙伴(Buddy)... 是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.86,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,潜水时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:41.33,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,一定要两个人一组一起潜水彼此协助的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.41,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,那个搭档就被称作(buddy)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.25,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,彼此协助的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:47.82,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:51.42,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,小闪光 我们也开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.37,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.88,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,确认BCD是否与身体紧密贴合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.88,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}BCD:Buoyancy Compensation Device:浮力补偿装备 通常是背心状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.43,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.48,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,气罐...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.18,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.76,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,确认配重带是否能迅速解开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.81,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.77,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,确认装备和器材没有缠绕打结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.77,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}他们两个人都是一副认真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.26,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.94,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,确认能否顺利通过调节器进行呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.94,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}调节器/Regulator:用于将气罐里的高压气体减压至适合人呼吸\N的水平的减压装置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:27.98,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.81,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,虽然完全不知道他们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.81,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}残压确认...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.76,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,但是感觉好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.33,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}...正常!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.50,Amanchu_Main,BS,0,0,0,,BCD OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.21,Amanchu_Main,LB,0,0,0,,气罐 OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.99,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那两个人也很熟练了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.18,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,闪光...那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.94,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,防寒头罩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.90,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,虽然4月了 海里还是很冷的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.23,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.52,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.44,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.79,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我气(去)啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.90,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯 多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.64,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,注意不要被海浪冲倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.66,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:26.12,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,无比快乐的世界正无限地向前延展着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:33.43,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,快乐的世界正在那里无限地延展着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.22,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,真好啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.19,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,伊豆这里的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:55.85,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,在4月到6月期间有着所谓的「春浊」现象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.62,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,春浊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:01.38,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,到了春天逐渐升温的海水里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:05.66,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,原生植物开始激增导致海水变得混浊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.89,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,换句话说 有点像是猪肉酱汤的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.01,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,猪肉酱汤?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:16.23,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,透明度急剧下降 从而导致视野变差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.86,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那样的海中景色还会有乐趣吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:28.53,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,这个时期可是「生命」开始的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:36.00,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,小鱼们为了吃繁茂的原生植物而来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:40.75,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,而大鱼们则会吃掉小鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:45.52,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,就这样 当这片大海再次满溢着生命的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.58,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,大海也就再次变得透明了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.76,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.93,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,可以看到生命的景色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:08:02.12,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,要是姑娘你在春浊结束的时候能下海潜水就再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.75,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:09.94,Amanchu_Main,K,0,0,0,,不过看今天的状况 能见度都不到一米呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.82,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,一米都不到?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.81,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,闪光没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.11,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,不会有危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.86,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.54,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我们回来啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.25,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.71,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,什～么都看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:31.63,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,为了不走散就已经竭尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.82,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,今天的难度真是太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.73,Amanchu_Main,BS,0,0,0,,只能看到前面人的脚蹼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.72,Amanchu_Main,LB,0,0,0,,真是性命攸关的潜水!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.94,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,有那么地...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:42.95,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,但是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:44.14,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.00,Amanchu_Main,BS,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.92,Amanchu_Main,Ta,0,0,0,,那就换上气罐开始第二潜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.19,Amanchu_Main,All,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:58.20,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,闪光他们应该都看不清海里的样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.79,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,却看上去非常地开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.14,Amanchu_Main_Top,Ta,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs44}这次走其他的路线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.94,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.09,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,会不会等得很无聊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.14,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.82,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,还听奶奶讲了很美妙的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.54,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,而且 听我说 闪光 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:25.10,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我也想能尽早下水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.83,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,为什么我的小裤裤会在那种地方!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.26,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,那个...这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:56.71,Amanchu_Main,LB,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:57.97,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,男的过来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.18,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.28,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,她明白了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.50,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.94,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,确实是千钧一发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.90,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.90,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,不过不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.95,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,小裤裤没事...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:46.05,Amanchu_Main,BS,0,0,0,,这样啊 原来她是那么想要猴子头套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.83,Amanchu_Main,BS,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:49.62,Amanchu_Main,BS,0,0,0,,送
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.41,Amanchu_Main,BS,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:51.54,Amanchu_Main,BS,0,0,0,,啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.11,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,讨厌...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.36,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,讨厌啦～!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.45,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:06.04,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,告诉我那位客人的联系方式!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.76,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,参加过闪光的潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:18.13,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,今天终于轮到我的泳池实践了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.12,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,天气晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.23,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,没有风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.43,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,没有云
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.98,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,也没有多少...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.47,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,从容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:28.10,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,那么首先进行伙伴确认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.00,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,伙伴确认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.58,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,BCD...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:38.47,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,气罐...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:41.05,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,气阀...确认OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.99,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,配重带(Weights)...确认OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:46.27,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,快卸类(Release)...确认OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.57,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,空气(Air)确认...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.82,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,来 吸气...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.40,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,呼气...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.40,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,能呼吸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:58.96,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.15,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,最终(Final)确认OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.15,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}这五步也被称作:BWRAF Begin With Review And Friend\NBCD Weight Release Air Final
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.24,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,闪光由我来确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.06,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,那就派(拜)托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:09.85,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好...好像不太像是伙伴确认呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.57,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,好了 做好准备了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:13.91,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.75,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.78,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,非常地...重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:22.84,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,啊 全部加起来将近有30公斤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.32,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,三十...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.83,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,下了水就觉得轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.19,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.00,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,不用着急慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.08,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.23,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,终于要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.93,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,无论什么都是第一次的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.29,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,心跳的好剧烈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:47.26,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,跨步式入水～!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:53.51,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.16,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.71,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.74,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,身体被重量往后拉...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.83,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,但还是能浮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:06.91,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,也就证明了有那么大的浮力在起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:07.70,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:14.28,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,然后把这根管子举起来 按下这个按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.15,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,把空气排出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.21,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.80,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.45,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好...好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:25.47,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,啊 刚才好像挺有伙伴的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:27.18,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,那么就 潜行!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.10,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,心跳的好剧烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:30.92,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.30,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.50,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,潜得越来越深了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:44.72,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,剧烈的心跳平息不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.70,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,咦...咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.20,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好像...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.27,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,小点?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.83,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,面罩里进水跑到鼻子里去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.61,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,潜水基本是靠嘴呼吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:37.42,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,就算面罩进了点水也不要去在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.89,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:42.04,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,首先得去适应水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.18,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,没事吧 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.58,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.52,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.83,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,那再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.49,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,Let us Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.87,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好难受...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.75,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,适...适应了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:26.67,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,必须适应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.36,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.90,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,如果这里是...10米深的水下呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:42.96,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.19,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好难受...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.08,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好可怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:49.61,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,小点?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.28,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.96,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,回忆一下讲义里的面罩除水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.74,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.26,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,那 再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:00.42,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,小点?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:04.96,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.65,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,水又进来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.22,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那个...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:20.02,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,按住面罩上部 稍微打开一点下部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.57,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,成功了 做到面罩除水了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.49,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,小点?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.75,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,做到面罩除水了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:39.98,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:44.10,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,水还是一个劲地往面罩里进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:47.10,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,没办法呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.69,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,可能再往下错错会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.22,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:55.30,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,果然是因为夹到头发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.82,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,形成空隙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:04.82,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,小点!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.26,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我...上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.56,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,小点!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.03,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,去做就能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.79,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,做不到的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.75,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,去做就能办到!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:25.63,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,一定能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.52,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:32.52,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,不去做的话就什么也办不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:48.59,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我只是...我只是...在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.32,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.74,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,但却没能把恐惧表达出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.54,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,想去做却没做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.37,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,结果没能办到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:11.56,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我到现在为止到底放弃了多少事情呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.10,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.46,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好可怕啊 闪光!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.04,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.03,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.41,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,别怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:29.70,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,有我跟你在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.23,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,别怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.39,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,水又...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.34,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,水不再进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.56,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.31,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,不再进水了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.34,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.87,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:20.77,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我现在正在水中呼吸着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.48,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,轻轻地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:34.14,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,轻轻盈盈 轻轻盈盈地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:39.00,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,蓝色的光芒温柔地将我怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:43.39,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我的身体在蔚蓝的空间中翻舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.81,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,凉凉地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:48.89,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,淙淙汨汨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:51.06,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,淙淙汨汨地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:17.62,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,若说我心中不再畏惧 就如同说谎一般...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.26,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,不过 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.22,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,有闪光在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:27.25,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,和闪光在一起就没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:30.41,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,潜水里有一条规矩～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:35.11,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,不论是什么样的高手都绝对不要一个人下水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.24,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,伙伴体制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.07,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,那意味着自己将担负起对方的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:44.13,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,也意味着将自己的生命托付给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.38,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:50.99,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.46,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,你们是「伙伴」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.06,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.53,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:19.13,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,成功了 你做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:19.69,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,闪光...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.62,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,小点 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:25.54,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.32,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,和她在一起的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:27.28,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,和闪光在一起的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.58,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,肯定可以无所不能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:31.66,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.17,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,咦? 奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.64,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,爬不上去...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.34,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,干式潜水服吸了水变重了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:52.28,Amanchu_Main,M,0,0,0,,小点还得培养一点基础体力呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:09.49,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}くれた言葉、ひとつ、笑顔、涙、ふたつ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:09.49,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,你给予的一句话 得到两副笑容与泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:20.00,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}胸の奥に満ちていく　寄せて返す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:20.00,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐充满内心 涌上来又返回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:30.01,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}ねぇ…側に眠る日常の種
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:30.01,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 在身边沉睡的 日常的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:41.77,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}光に触れて咲く目覚める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:41.77,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,碰触到光而绽开 觉醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:51.61,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}蒼の心　蒼の世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:51.61,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色的心中 蓝色的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:23:12.63,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}宝物ばかりで私と貴方を包んだ まるで小さな海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:23:12.63,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,全是宝物 包围着我和你 仿佛就像小小的海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:23.85,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}出逢えたね　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:23.85,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,我们相遇了呢 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:30.42,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,这样恐怖的体验对我来说也是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:32.80,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,所以要把这个这样再这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:34.76,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,下一回 蓝海少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:40.92,Amanchu_Next_Ep_Title,Next Episode Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,1)}同伴与第一次的大海的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:36.81,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,同伴与第一次的大海的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:39.89,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,要把哪个怎么样再怎么样?
